nodes.text: Goodrow Neb Nob was a Gungan who lived during the last decades of the Galactic Republic. By 33 BBY, Neb Nob lived in Otoh Gunga, the capital city of the Gungan society, under the rule of Boss Rugor Nass. That year, Neb Nob worked at the Otoh Gunga Traffic Control and once reported that a seaquake was located five kilometers south of Boss Nass's position.
